<br>
&quot;Yasoo! Welcome to Sarmatia, glad to have you in our tribe. Feeling better? A trip to Hades Throne Room doesn't always leave people in high spirits.&quot;<br>
<br>
She laughed a little. No matter what, she could never manage to make her greeting short. Like Queen Hippolyte had once said, she could talk for days. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=tiger4157>Tiger4157</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 82<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(1/4/01 9:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=29.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New to Sarmatia</span><hr size=1> ::looks to Gabrielle and smiles with a chuckle:: <br>
