<br>
&quot;Yeah.. you'd think he'd be more grateful after Xena and I recaptured that dead guy who stole his magic helmet.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=tiger4157>Tiger4157</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 83<br> <font color=#8A2BE2>(1/6/01 5:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=29.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New to Sarmatia</span><hr size=1> ::nods::<br>
